description:
An additional design for Barren, Laty, and Lac's outfits. Changes the appearance of the main characters from Voice of Cards: The Forsaken Maiden. 
*The appearance will not change in some sections.
*This content is also available for sale as part of a set. Please take care not to re-purchase the same products.
name: Voice of Cards: The Forsaken Maiden Puppets' Costume
